## **8. `sigma/_TEMPLATE.yml`**
```yaml
title: <Rule descriptive name>
description: <Short and precise description>
status: experimental
level: <low | medium | high | critical>
author: Bastian-Sec
date: YYYY-MM-DD
references:
  - <https://reference.link>
tags:
  - topic:<IP | Ports | DNS | HTTP>

logsource:
  product: <windows | linux | any>
  service: <service_name>

detection:
  selection:
    <FieldName>: <Value>
  condition: selection

falsepositives:
  - <Known benign cases>
